snippet.title: Become a racing GP manager now and test your skills against thousands online!
snippet.description:
Get in the shoes of Toto Wolff, Mattia Binotto and Christian Horner. Manage your racing team against thousands of racing managers from all over the world. The only online motorsport manager game without any pay-to-win features. Now available on iOS and Android devices!
https://gpro.net
